    "description": "极具氛围感的心理恐怖，搭配令人怀念的VHS风格，定能让你沉浸其中。在一家偏僻的公路餐厅扮演一名夜班女服务员，接待陌生顾客，体会逐渐加深的恐惧感。每到夜晚，梦魇都变得愈发真实，某人正从黑暗中窥视你。你能活下来吗？<br>本作是该系列的第一章，更多章节即将到来。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >一个你我都可能面临的困境</h2>18岁少女玛丽被迫搬出父母的家，在一家公路餐厅当女服务员，藉此赚钱来付房租和餐费。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264210/extras/f7226d2f85f6c07bac7f371e6839f06e.poster.avif?t=1730575973\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264210/extras/f7226d2f85f6c07bac7f371e6839f06e.webm?t=1730575973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264210/extras/f7226d2f85f6c07bac7f371e6839f06e.mp4?t=1730575973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >当好一名女服务员</h2>事件发生时，你是值夜班的唯一员工。接单，准备食物，接待顾客，夜班结束时还要记得打扫卫生。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264210/extras/52cba0f073aae5a9743985e5726d8a8d.poster.avif?t=1730575973\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264210/extras/52cba0f073aae5a9743985e5726d8a8d.webm?t=1730575973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264210/extras/52cba0f073aae5a9743985e5726d8a8d.mp4?t=1730575973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >驾车前往你需要去的地方</h2>住在拖车公园对于上班来说实属不易，好在可以买到一辆便宜的车。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264210/extras/44ce84c4f2d4f99a48191f18c7d39a93.poster.avif?t=1730575973\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264210/extras/44ce84c4f2d4f99a48191f18c7d39a93.webm?t=1730575973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264210/extras/44ce84c4f2d4f99a48191f18c7d39a93.mp4?t=1730575973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与顾客以及周遭之人交谈</h2>在与人打交道的过程中，你总能听到许多新鲜有趣的事情，这些信息或许会在恰当的时候派上用场。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264210/extras/4a7d8da3d87f7b8fece9757ffae137b9.poster.avif?t=1730575973\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264210/extras/4a7d8da3d87f7b8fece9757ffae137b9.webm?t=1730575973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264210/extras/4a7d8da3d87f7b8fece9757ffae137b9.mp4?t=1730575973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >某人正在窥视你</h2>夜幕降临时，恐惧感逐渐加深，你甚至感觉某人正从黑暗中窥视你……或许这种感觉并非空穴来风。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264210/extras/1c5d1c66291904c98a44faf4a6e58905.poster.avif?t=1730575973\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264210/extras/1c5d1c66291904c98a44faf4a6e58905.webm?t=1730575973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264210/extras/1c5d1c66291904c98a44faf4a6e58905.mp4?t=1730575973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>充满氛围感的环境。<br></li><li>VHS影片风格。<br></li><li>心理恐怖。<br></li><li>沉浸式体验。</li></ul>",
